strategy: Implement a three-stage optimization: 1) Pre-filter fact table using derived constraints from dimension tables, 2) Perform early partial aggregation at the store-date level, 3) Join with dimension tab
what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, single_pass_aggregation, pushdown achieving 1.32x speedup
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators
